{"tid":2184355,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"明年文憑試延至 4.23 開考、7.21放榜　考期縮短　取消中、英文科口試　校本評核取消或減佔分","createTime":"2020-09-01T13:07:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T21:30:02.000Z","uid":359022,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"35a432b47de8563322aec632caab6661d302fbc7","tid":2184355,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/明年文憑試延至-4-23-開考-7-21放榜-考期縮短-取消中-英文科口試-校本評核取消或減佔分/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%BB%B6%E8%87%B3-4-23-%E9%96%8B%E8%80%83-7-21%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C-%E8%80%83%E6%9C%9F%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%A3%E8%A9%A6-%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%AC%E8%A9%95%E6%A0%B8%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%88%96%E6%B8%9B%E4%BD%94%E5%88%86%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYb%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=1f8964c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%BB%B6%E8%87%B3-4-23-%E9%96%8B%E8%80%83-7-21%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C-%E8%80%83%E6%9C%9F%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%A3%E8%A9%A6-%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%AC%E8%A9%95%E6%A0%B8%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%88%96%E6%B8%9B%E4%BD%94%E5%88%86%2F&h=d2fd85f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/明年文憑試延至-4-23-開考-7-21放榜-考期縮短-取消中-英文科口試-校本評核取消或減佔分/</a><br />\n<br />\n漢肺炎疫情持續，全港學校斷續停課，影響教學及備戰文憑試。考評局今（1 日）宣佈 2021 年文憑試應變及精簡方案，來年文憑試甲類科目由以往 3 月底至 4 月初開考，延至 4 月 23 日開考，整個考期由四個半星期，縮短到三個半星期，至 5 月 17日完成，同時會取消中文及英文科口試，各科校本評核（SBA）取消、或減少佔分比例，預計來年 7 月 21 日放榜。<br />\n<br />\n根據精簡方案，考評局一共修訂了 23 個甲類科目的考核內容或佔分比例，包括取消 9 科校本評核（SBA），包括中國文學、英國文學、生物、化學、物理、組合科學、綜合科學、健康管理與社會關懷、資訊及通訊科技，其餘 5 科 SBA，包括中文科、通識科佔分比例，分別由 20% 減至 10%，英文、設計與應用科技、音樂科的 SBA 將減量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />SBA Am I A Joke<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3d1cae382fd8da32a50718f0c68e6eacb6ba34","tid":2184355,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:08:32.000Z","msg":"IES <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5573eaf4ae50c3651d268dd690756b25f0e4cf54","tid":2184355,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"135007521961b9a07655946839db7900bd440f57","tid":2184355,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35a432b47de8563322aec632caab6661d302fbc7","tid":2184355,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T13:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/明年文憑試延至-4-23-開考-7-21放榜-考期縮短-取消中-英文科口試-校本評核取消或減佔分/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%BB%B6%E8%87%B3-4-23-%E9%96%8B%E8%80%83-7-21%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C-%E8%80%83%E6%9C%9F%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%A3%E8%A9%A6-%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%AC%E8%A9%95%E6%A0%B8%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E6%88%96%E6%B8%9B%E4%BD%94%E5%88%86%2F&d=H6IDb39AroI58YjM1eqeYb%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=1f8964c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%87%E6%86%91%E8%A9%A6%E5%BB%B6%E8%87%B3-4-23-%E9%96%8B%E8%80%83-7-21%E6%94%BE%E6%A6%9C-%E8%80%83%E6%9C%9F%E7%B8%AE%E7%9F%AD-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%B8%AD-%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E7%A7%91%E5%8F%A3%E8%A9%A6-%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%AC%E8%